com.github.bordertech.wcomponents.util

Class InternalMessages

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.bordertech.wcomponents.util.InternalMessages

  • public final class InternalMessages
extends Object
    This class declares constants for internal messages issued by the WComponent framework itself. The default messages themeselves are contained in a WComponent configuration properties file. Developers who are internationalising an application should also internationalise these messages.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Yiannis Paschalidis
